------------------- THE HIVES COMPLETE DISCOGRAPHY 1997-2010 -------------------


Every album and every single from the Swedish garage punk rock sensation, The Hives.


All songs are in MP3 format, and album artwork is included. The tags have been properly edited for iTunes and other compatible media players, and the song names have been properly edited for use on tag-incompatible media players. Just plug and play! This torrent includes;


- Barely Legal ............................................... [1997] {@192kbps}

- Veni Vidi Vicious .......................................... [2000] {@256kbps}

- Your New Favourite Band .................................... [2002] {@192kbps}

- Tyrannosaurus Hives ........................................ [2004] {@320kbps)

- The Hives Meet the Norm (Single)(UK Bonus Track)............ [2004] {@192kbps}

- Up Tight (Single)(UK Bonus Track) .......................... [2004] {@192kbps}

- Genepool Convulsions (Single) .............................. [2004] {@192kbps}

- The Black and White Album .................................. [2007] {@320kbps}

- Fall Is Just Something Grownups Invented (Bonus Track) ..... [2007] {@320kbps}

- Throw It On Me (Timbaland ft. The Hives) ................... [2007] {@192kbps}

- A Christmas Duel (Single)(Cyndi Lauper and The Hives) ...... [2008] {@192kbps)

- Black, White and Run (Nike+ Original Remix) ................ [2008] {@192kbps}

- Tarred and Feathered EP .................................... [2010] {@192kbps}


NOTE: I did not include the singles that are already included in an album.

